1
00:00:09,340 --> 00:00:12,410
You're my father?

2
00:00:12,580 --> 00:00:14,250
Even though you're not
my legitimate child,

3
00:00:14,250 --> 00:00:16,180
I will still
provide for you as best I can.

4
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:18,620
Your tuition and living expenses...

5
00:00:18,650 --> 00:00:21,490
Mom said she
scraped it together from her savings.

6
00:00:21,490 --> 00:00:23,820
To protect you
from the outside world,

7
00:00:24,460 --> 00:00:27,460
I had her watch over you
and report back to me.

8
00:00:28,090 --> 00:00:30,530
Including details about
the person you're seeing now.

9
00:00:30,530 --> 00:00:33,130
I absolutely forbid you
from being with another woman.

10
00:00:33,130 --> 00:00:34,200
What gives you the right...?

11
00:00:34,230 --> 00:00:35,770
I'm doing this for your own good.

12
00:00:35,770 --> 00:00:37,900
To ensure you
can live a happy life.

13
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:39,240
Who are you
to decide what makes me happy...?

14
00:00:39,310 --> 00:00:40,670
It doesn't matter what you say.

15
00:00:40,670 --> 00:00:44,340
To protect your happiness,
I'll do whatever it takes.

16
00:00:44,540 --> 00:00:45,780
What do you mean by that?

17
00:00:45,780 --> 00:00:47,310
I mean exactly what I said.

18
00:00:47,380 --> 00:00:50,680
When the time is right,
you will marry the man I choose.

19
00:00:50,680 --> 00:00:52,720
Once you've produced an heir,

20
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:55,320
you'll be set for life
and live happily.

21
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:57,420
A child...

22
00:00:57,420 --> 00:00:58,890
In my entire life,

23
00:00:58,890 --> 00:01:00,190
I've never been in love with anyone.

24
00:01:00,260 --> 00:01:03,460
Sami,
remember this promise.

25
00:01:03,730 --> 00:01:07,100
I will eliminate anyone or anything
that stands in your way.

26
00:01:07,130 --> 00:01:10,100
And I keep my promises.

27
00:01:10,300 --> 00:01:13,010
After that,
it was one nightmare after another.
